  "text": "In case when there exists a relation between the two classes it is also possible to generate a rule [CITATION_1] . For example, there are \"Son\" and \"Father\" classes and also the \"hasParent\" relation between these two classes. In this case it becomes possible to generate the rule [CITATION_2] :",
